doctype html
html(lang="es")
  head
    meta(charset="UTF-8")
    title Security Scan Report
    link(rel="stylesheet", href="/stylesheets/report.css")
  body
    section.cover
      div.header
        img(src="{{agencyLogo}}", alt="Agency Logo", style="width:48px;height:48px;object-fit:contain")
        // <img src="../public/images/logo_prueba.png" style="width:48px; height:48px; margin-right:12px;" />
        div.header-text
          h1 Security Report
          p Automated Web Security Scan

      h1 Frontend Security Report
      div.score-wrapper
        div.score-circle.score-medium
          div.score-value #{score}
          div.score-label #{scoreLabel}

      p.cover-date Date of analysis: #{reportDate}

    div.page-break

    header.header
      div.meta
        h1 Frontend Security Report
        p Preventive security review before delivery or production launch

        ul
          li
            strong Client:
            |  #{clientName}
          li
            strong Site analyzed:
            |  #{siteUrl}
          li
            strong Date:
            |  #{reportDate}

    section.summary
      h2 Executive Summary
      p
        | An automated frontend security analysis was performed on the evaluated site,
        | with the objective of identifying configurations and practices that could represent
        | risks before their exposure in production.

      p
        | The analysis focused on security policies, HTTP header configuration
        | and exposure of JavaScript resources.

    section.findings
      h2 Findings Detected

      table
        thead
          tr
            th Severity
            th Find
            th Impact
        tbody
          | #{findingsRows}

    section.recommendations
      h2 Recommendations

      ul
        li Implement appropriate HTTP security policies to reduce common risks.
        li Review the exposure of JavaScript files and build configurations.
        li Incorporar este tipo de revisi√≥n como parte del proceso de entrega.

    footer.footer
      p
        | This report is based on an automated analysis and does not replace a complete manual security audit.

      p.cta
        | For a deeper review or support in implementing improvements,
        | we recommend a detailed technical evaluation.